    "description": "Three Finger Battle Arena is a game where you can punch your friends into orbit, then swing away like nothing ever happened!<br><br>Features include: <br><br><strong>Three game modes! (and growing)</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/9d9e225a77131b9ab49c896dfcba2037.poster.avif?t=1645990684\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/9d9e225a77131b9ab49c896dfcba2037.webm?t=1645990684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/9d9e225a77131b9ab49c896dfcba2037.mp4?t=1645990684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Grapple and punch!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/7c2a095be43754fb46dd8463d8c3f855.poster.avif?t=1645990684\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/7c2a095be43754fb46dd8463d8c3f855.webm?t=1645990684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/7c2a095be43754fb46dd8463d8c3f855.mp4?t=1645990684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Up to 8 players!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/9a9051ddd08fcc5dc1ad3720efe2f744.poster.avif?t=1645990684\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/9a9051ddd08fcc5dc1ad3720efe2f744.webm?t=1645990684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893860/extras/9a9051ddd08fcc5dc1ad3720efe2f744.mp4?t=1645990684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game modes currently are:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Battle Arena - Avoid falling off platforms and knock other players off the stage.<br></li><li>Floor is Lava - Battle Arena but lava is slowly rising, avoid it! <br></li><li>Spleef - Smash blocks and punch your friends, try to make the other players fall in the lava.</li></ul>",
